{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset's sample interval is set to once per day.",
    "The entire electricity consumption value is represented in the dataset as rows, while the electricity consumption value for a certain day is provided as a column.",
    "Moreover, statistics are gathered during onsite inspections.",
    "However, the electricity consumption dataset comprises outliers, missing values, and extremely dispersed data.",
    "These irregularities must be corrected before developing the ETD model."
  ]
}